get.description:
Retrieve possible winning of a wager

Possible error codes:

| *Code* |          *Description*                                                |
|--------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------|
| 4000   |  Coupon requested is expired                                          |
| 4001   |	Coupon requested is not winning                                      |
| 4003   |  Coupon is paid by same agency/retailer                               |
| 4004   |  Coupon is paid by other agency/retailer                              |
| 4013   |  Coupon is winning but the amount is not payable                      |
| 10001  |	Draw requested not found                                             |
| 10004  |	Draw not held yet                                                    |
| 10008  |  Draw is not payable yet                                              |
| 10012  |  Draw completed, winning numbers entered, but draw is not payable yet |
| 18001  |	Invalid provider                                                     |
| 18002  |	No terminal defined or available                                     |
| 109999 |  Connection with CS is down                                           |
| 400013 |  Dynamically created description for a missing header/query parameter |
| 500014 |  Transaction timeouts                                                 |
